========,2,Ethnic groups.
The people in the province are mainly indigenous citizens of Quechua descent.
Quechua is the language which the majority of the population (65.11%) learnt to speak in childhood, 34.51% of the residents started speaking using the Spanish language (2007 Peru Census).
